xcerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"The best people are those of my generation, then those who come after them, then those who come after them. Then, there will come people after them whose testimony precedes their oaths and their oaths precede their\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33050,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/02\/swear-by-allah-or-keep-quiet\/","url_meta":{"origin":26052,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: Swear by Allah or keep quiet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, found Umar ibn al-Khattab while he was upon his mount, swearing an oath by his father. The Prophet said, \u201cSurely Allah prohibits you from swearing an oath by your fathers. Whoever swears an oath, let him\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31743,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/not-swear-many-oaths\/","url_meta":{"origin":26052,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: Do not swear many oaths for your business","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of swearing many oaths while trading. Verily, it helps trade but erases the blessing.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1607 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Nawawi said, \u201cIn this is the prohibition of swearing many oaths while trading,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15415,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/prophet-seven-commands\/","url_meta":{"origin":26052,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ahkam: Seven prohibitions and commands","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara' ibn 'Azib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited us from seven things: using gold rings, silk, flax, brocade, red saddle clothes, taffeta, and silver vessels. And the Prophet commanded us to do seven things: to visit the sick, to follow the funeral procession, to bless\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14667,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/09\/false-oaths-suicide-cursing-takfir\/","url_meta":{"origin":26052,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sins: False oaths, suicide, cursing, excommunication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Thabit ibn al-Dahhak reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever swears falsely by a religion other than Islam, he is what he has professed. Whoever kills himself with something, he will be punished with it in the fire of Hell. Cursing a believer is like killing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24958,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/prophet-oath-turner-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":26052,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: I swear by the turner of the hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The oath of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was, \u201cNo, by the turner of the hearts!\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6253 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0642\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0650\u0628\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0628\u0650 6253 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d \u0627\u0644\u0628\u062e\u0627\u0631\u064a \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26052","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/